---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import Divider from '../components/Divider.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About · neural-bridge.dev">
  <header class="mb-10 pt-4">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-rust-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">// About</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96, 'SOFT' 60;">Andy Herman</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <p>
      I'm Andy. I'm curious about agentic AI tools: what they can do, where they break, how to make them actually useful in daily work. This site is where I write about that exploration. The agents I'm building, the decisions I make out loud, the experiments that work and the ones that don't.
    </p>
    <p>
      The current main project is <a href="/projects/neural-bridge">Neural Bridge</a>, a personal AI substrate that lets specialized agents share memory and compound across sessions instead of starting fresh every time. Future projects land here as they begin.
    </p>
    <p>
      Most of the writing cross-posts to LinkedIn where the audiences overlap.
    </p>

    <h2>Find me</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/andy-herman">GitHub</a></li>
      <li>LinkedIn (TBD)</li>
      <li>Support the writing: <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/neuralbridge">buymeacoffee.com/neuralbridge</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <Divider />

  <p class="font-serif italic text-center text-cream-800 dark:text-cream-200">
    "The work of using the system is the work of building it."
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
